sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Chat UI
    participant Runtime as agents-runtime
    participant Agent as Agent + tools

    User->>UI: Open /chat
    UI->>Runtime: GET /threads
    Runtime-->>UI: Thread list
    User->>UI: Send prompt
    UI->>Runtime: POST /threads/{id}/messages
    UI->>Runtime: POST /threads/{id}/runs?stream=true
    Runtime->>Agent: Run agent
    Agent-->>Runtime: Tool output and answer deltas
    Runtime-->>UI: Server-sent events
    UI-->>User: Render streaming answer and citations
